appealed to the countries in southern Africa to enhance their unity
to meet challenges in national development.
</P>
<P>
The southern African region must promote at all times regional
solidarity and unity among the people, Nujoma said when
officially opening the Zambia International Trade Fair in Ndola,
capital of Zambia's Copperbelt Province.
</P>
