maintain the culture of frequent consultations and exchange of
information among themselves in order to consolidate and cement the
unity between governments and peoples.
</P>
<P>
As for specific relations between Namibia and Zambia, Nujoma
proposed the establishment of a working group to co-ordinate the
Valvis Bay-Ndola growth in Namibia and Zambia.
</P>
<P>
