<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major World Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 6 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 11 major world
cities from 20:00 today to 20:00 on July 7, issued by China's
Central Meteorological Station tonight:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. 21 degrees c., max. 34 degrees c., clear to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tokyo: min. 27 degrees c., max. 36 degrees c., clear to cloudy,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Bangkok: min. 26 degrees c., max. 35 degrees c., cloudy, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Sydney: min. 10 degrees c., max. 16 degrees c., drizzle to
clear, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Karachi: min. 28 degrees c., max. 35 degrees c., cloudy, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
